Subject: Re: [T2] case splitting tool

On 12/8/03 3:07 PM, "Richard Atwell" <ratwell(-at-)mac.com> wrote:

> What's the best tool to use to split a a Type 4 case? Does the Type I case
> splitting tool fit in the Type 4 oil pump cavity?

Yes, it will fit, the bores are the same size.

Splitting the case should never be so difficult that you need this tool,
however. A few sharp blows on the fan mounts with 2 rubber mallets (used
together, in opposite directions) works.

Scott
